html
<script>
    function showMessage() {
        alert('Hello, world!');
    }
</script>
<button onclick="showMessage()">Click me</button>

``html
<script src="script.js"></script>
<button onclick="showMessage()">Click me</button>
```
`script.js` file:
```javascript
function showMessage() {
    alert('Hello, world!');
}

